title: Composite Index of Three Lagging Indicators, Amplitude-Adjusted, Weighted for United States
notes:
Components Of This Index Are (Diffusion Index, Manuufacturers' Sales), (Diffusion Index, New Orders For Durable Goods), And (Diffusion Index, Freight Carloadings). Source: U.S. Bureau Of The Census

This NBER data series m16005 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 16 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter16.html.
